---
import ButtonFreeAssessment from './ButtonFreeAssessment.astro';
interface Props {
  bgColor?: string;
  bgPattern?: string;
  showDotMatrix?: boolean;
}

const {
  bgColor = 'bg-white'
} = Astro.props;
---

<section class={`py-16 md:py-24 px-4 ${bgColor}`}>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
      <!-- Left: Content -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Signs Your Arizona Roof May Qualify for Insurance Coverage</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8">Arizona's extreme weather takes a toll on roofs. Here are the most common types of damage we find during inspections:</p>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#76ba41]">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12 2.25c-5.385 0-9.75 4.365-9.75 9.75s4.365 9.75 9.75 9.75 9.75-4.365 9.75-9.75S17.385 2.25 12 2.25ZM12.75 6a.75.75 0 0 0-1.5 0v6c0 .414.336.75.75.75h4.5a.75.75 0 0 0 0-1.5h-3.75V6Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Monsoon Wind Damage</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">High winds during monsoon season can lift, tear, or completely remove shingles from your roof.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#76ba41]">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="m6.72 5.66 11.62 11.62A8.25 8.25 0 0 0 6.72 5.66Zm10.56 12.68L5.66 6.72a8.25 8.25 0 0 0 11.62 11.62ZM5.105 5.106c3.807-3.808 9.98-3.808 13.788 0 3.808 3.807 3.808 9.98 0 13.788-3.807 3.808-9.98 3.808-13.788 0-3.808-3.807-3.808-9.98 0-13.788Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Hail Impact</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Hailstones create dents and cracks in shingles that compromise your roof's integrity.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#76ba41]">
                  <path d="M12 2.25a.75.75 0 0 1 .75.75v2.25a.75.75 0 0 1-1.5 0V3a.75.75 0 0 1 .75-.75ZM7.5 12a4.5 4.5 0 1 1 9 0 4.5 4.5 0 0 1-9 0ZM18.894 6.166a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06-1.06l-1.591 1.59a.75.75 0 1 0 1.06 1.061l1.591-1.59ZM21.75 12a.75.75 0 0 1-.75.75h-2.25a.75.75 0 0 1 0-1.5H21a.75.75 0 0 1 .75.75ZM17.834 18.894a.75.75 0 0 0 1.06-1.06l-1.59-1.591a.75.75 0 1 0-1.061 1.06l1.59 1.591ZM12 18a.75.75 0 0 1 .75.75V21a.75.75 0 0 1-1.5 0v-2.25A.75.75 0 0 1 12 18ZM7.758 17.303a.75.75 0 0 0-1.061-1.06l-1.591 1.59a.75.75 0 0 0 1.06 1.061l1.591-1.59ZM6 12a.75.75 0 0 1-.75.75H3a.75.75 0 0 1 0-1.5h2.25A.75.75 0 0 1 6 12ZM6.697 7.757a.75.75 0 0 0 1.06-1.06l-1.59-1.591a.75.75 0 0 0-1.061 1.06l1.59 1.591Z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Extreme Heat Cracking</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Arizona's intense sun causes shingles to dry out, crack, and become brittle over time.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#76ba41]">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.97 14.316H5.004c-.322 0-.64-.08-.925-.232a2.022 2.022 0 0 1-.717-.645 2.108 2.108 0 0 1-.242-1.883l2.36-7.201C5.769 3.54 5.96 3 7.365 3c2.072 0 4.276.678 6.156 1.256.473.145.925.284 1.35.404h.114v9.862a25.485 25.485 0 0 0-4.238 5.514c-.197.376-.516.67-.901.83a1.74 1.74 0 0 1-1.21.048 1.79 1.79 0 0 1-.96-.757 1.867 1.867 0 0 1-.269-1.211l1.562-4.63ZM19.822 14H17V6a2 2 0 1 1 4 0v6.823c0 .65-.527 1.177-1.177 1.177Z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Missing/Curled Shingles</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Heat and weather cause shingles to curl up at the edges or go missing entirely.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#76ba41]">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.5 12a1.5 1.5 0 1 1 3 0 1.5 1.5 0 0 1-3 0Zm6 0a1.5 1.5 0 1 1 3 0 1.5 1.5 0 0 1-3 0Zm6 0a1.5 1.5 0 1 1 3 0 1.5 1.5 0 0 1-3 0Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Granule Loss</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Shingle granules protect your roof from UV damage. Excessive loss means it's time for replacement.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#76ba41]">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M9.0276 4.36983C9.84851 3.59377 10.8715 3 12.05 3c1.1786 0 2.2016.59377 3.0225 1.36983.8255.78038 1.5331 1.82292 2.1072 2.92578C18.3188 9.48385 19.05 12.1425 19.05 14c0 3.866-3.134 7-7 7-3.86594 0-6.99995-3.134-6.99995-7 0-1.8575.73123-4.51615 1.87035-6.70439.57411-1.10286 1.28173-2.1454 2.1072-2.92578Zm2.8023 5.91657c.3082-.45832.1865-1.07968-.2718-1.38786-.4583-.30818-1.0797-.18648-1.3879.27182-.37473.55732-.66096 1.25684-.85365 1.91184-.19234.6537-.31649 1.3484-.31649 1.9178 0 .5523.44772 1 1.00004 1 .5522 0 1-.4477 1-1 0-.3189.0769-.8156.2351-1.3533.1579-.5365.3717-1.0286.5947-1.3603Z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Water Stains/Leaks</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Interior water damage is often a sign of underlying roof problems covered by insurance.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#76ba41]">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M2 12C2 6.477 6.477 2 12 2s10 4.477 10 10-4.477 10-10 10S2 17.523 2 12Zm11-4a1 1 0 1 0-2 0v5a1 1 0 1 0 2 0V8Zm-1 7a1 1 0 1 0 0 2h.01a1 1 0 1 0 0-2H12Z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Sagging Roof Lines</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Visible sagging or dips in your roof indicate serious structural issues requiring immediate attention.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-3 mb-8">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#76ba41]">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M11.484 2.17a.75.75 0 0 1 1.032 0 11.209 11.209 0 0 0 7.877 3.08.75.75 0 0 1 .722.515 12.74 12.74 0 0 1 .635 3.985c0 5.942-4.064 10.933-9.563 12.348a.749.749 0 0 1-.374 0C6.314 20.683 2.25 15.692 2.25 9.75c0-1.39.223-2.73.635-3.985a.75.75 0 0 1 .722-.516l.143.001c2.996 0 5.718-1.17 7.734-3.08ZM12 8.25a.75.75 0 0 1 .75.75v3.75a.75.75 0 0 1-1.5 0V9a.75.75 0 0 1 .75-.75ZM12 15a.75.75 0 0 0-.75.75v.008c0 .414.336.75.75.75h.008a.75.75 0 0 0 .75-.75v-.008a.75.75 0 0 0-.75-.75H12Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Damaged Flashing</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Flashing protects vulnerable areas. When damaged, water can penetrate and cause extensive damage.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-[#76ba41] p-4 rounded">
            <p class="text-slate-900 font-semibold">
              Not sure if you have damage? Our free inspection will tell you exactly what's covered.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Right: Image + Button -->
      <div class="md:hidden mb-8">
        <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md mb-6">
          <img 
            src="https://RebelApeCDN.b-cdn.net/CTI-Roofing/roof-inspection-horizontal.webp"
            alt="Roof inspection"
            class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <ButtonFreeAssessment />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hidden md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-start md:gap-6">
        <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md h-[550px]">
          <img 
            src="https://RebelApeCDN.b-cdn.net/CTI-Roofing/roof-inspection-vertical.webp"
            alt="Roof inspection"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex justify-center md:justify-start">
          <ButtonFreeAssessment />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>